            <h1>What is Recursion?</h1>
        </div>

        <div class="content">
            <h2 class="content-subhead"></h2>
            <p>
                Recursion is the technique of solving a large problem by breaking it down into smaller sub-problems of the same kind. More precisely, it consists of what we call a <b>base case</b> and a <b>recursive case</b>.
            </p>
            
